		<item>
		<title>שבוע הירחים הפתוחים &#8211; הזוכים בתחרויות הבתים והחוות</title>
		<link>http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/?p=4858&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=%25d7%25a9%25d7%2591%25d7%2595%25d7%25a2-%25d7%2594%25d7%2599%25d7%25a8%25d7%2597%25d7%2599%25d7%259d-%25d7%2594%25d7%25a4%25d7%25aa%25d7%2595%25d7%2597%25d7%2599%25d7%259d-%25d7%2594%25d7%2596%25d7%2595%25d7%259b%25d7%2599%25d7%259d-%25d7%2591%25d7%25aa%25d7%2597%25d7%25a8%25d7%2595%25d7%2599%25d7%2595%25d7%25aa-%25d7%2594</link>
		<comments>http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/?p=4858#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 23 Aug 2011 08:58:57 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[אקו-ניוז]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/?p=4858</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[
שבוע הירחים הפתוחים הסתיים, והגיע הזמן להכריז על הזוכים!
.
נפתח בתחרות הבתים היפים:
במקום הראשון&#8230;

.
במקום השני&#8230;


.
במקום השלישי&#8230;



.
.
והזוכים בתחרות החוות המטופחות הם:
במקום הראשון&#8230;

.
במקום השני&#8230;


.
במקום השלישי&#8230;



.
.

]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/OpenMoons.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-2250 aligncenter" title="OpenMoons" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/OpenMoons.jpg" alt="" width="467" height="68" /></a></p>
<h3 style="direction: rtl;">שבוע הירחים הפתוחים הסתיים, והגיע הזמן להכריז על הזוכים!</h3>
<p style="direction: rtl;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">נפתח בתחרות הבתים היפים</span>:</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><strong>במקום הראשון&#8230;</strong></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerI.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4865" title="HomesSummerI" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerI.png" alt="" width="462" height="290" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><strong>במקום השני&#8230;</strong></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerII2.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4866" title="HomesSummerII2" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerII2.png" alt="" width="474" height="245" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerII2.bmp"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4877" title="HomesSummerII2" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerII2.bmp" alt="" width="450" height="255" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><strong>במקום השלישי&#8230;</strong></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerIII1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4867" title="HomesSummerIII1" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerIII1.png" alt="" width="467" height="291" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerIII2.bmp"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4868" title="HomesSummerIII2" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerIII2.bmp" alt="" width="456" height="260" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerIII3.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4869" title="HomesSummerIII3" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/HomesSummerIII3.png" alt="" width="448" height="282" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: right;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">והזוכים בתחרות החוות המטופחות הם</span>:</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><strong>במקום הראשון&#8230;</strong></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerI.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4859" title="FarmsSummerI" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerI.png" alt="" width="458" height="248" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><strong>במקום השני&#8230;</strong></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerII1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4860" title="FarmsSummerII1" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerII1.png" alt="" width="441" height="271" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerII2.bmp"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4861" title="FarmsSummerII2" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerII2.bmp" alt="" width="495" height="239" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><strong>במקום השלישי&#8230;</strong></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerIII1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4862" title="FarmsSummerIII1" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerIII1.png" alt="" width="470" height="293" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerIII2.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4863" title="FarmsSummerIII2" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerIII2.png" alt="" width="468" height="294" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerIII3.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4864" title="FarmsSummerIII3" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/FarmsSummerIII3.png" alt="" width="499" height="311" /></a></p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">.</p>
<p style="direction: rtl; text-align: center;">
]]></content:encoded>
